responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "E019F41545E12B3BD46CEBB2FE114A2A", "One who help us, there is. He hold knowledge we need, but not part of tribe's politics. Wisdom he have, sought by many, those who walk old path, and those who seek new. He understand spirits like few do, his guidance save us in past. His name T'kano, elder live near still water, in place of peace and silence.")
